column7: Germany-based Allianz primarily provides property casualty and life and health insurance, and asset management products and services worldwide. Allianz was established in 1890 and is headquartered in Munich, Germany.

Humanwell Healthcare provides healthcare solutions in the Asia-Pacific, North America, Europe, and Africa. It offers anesthetic products; biological products for cancer, anemia by chronic renal failure, hives and infectious hepatitis, and injuries and burn; and herbal medicines for cold and flu, rheumatoid arthritis, skin care, hepatitis, urinary tract infection, and hypomnesis.  The company was formerly known as Wuhan Humanwell Healthcare and changed its name to Humanwell Healthcare in March 2013. The company was founded in 1993 and is based in Wuhan, China.
